The user is on .NET 10 SDK and wants to know how to set up native MTP support. Based on the skill context:

On .NET 10+, instead of using `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` (which is the .NET 9 and earlier approach), you add a `test` section to `global.json`:

```json
{
  "sdk": {
    "version": "10.0.100"
  },
  "test": {
    "runner": "Microsoft.Testing.Platform"
  }
}
```

And you can remove `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` from the csproj.


